Important Limitation
Checksum is not guaranteed 100% unique.
Example rare case:
Plain text
Copy code
Data A → checksum 1234
Data B → checksum 1234
This is called hash collision.
Rare but possible.
Production Validation Strategy
For large migrations (50M rows):
Plain text
Copy code
Step 1  Row count validation
Step 2  Partition row count validation
Step 3  Partition checksum validation
Step 4  EXCEPT comparison
This guarantees 100% validation.
